<emphasis id="B2DAC79663432952A49C2422C6260C75" italics="true" pageId="27" pageNumber="28">
<pageBreakToken id="1653F66087D2045100A2B2BE582FF8BF" pageId="27" pageNumber="28" start="start">albescens</pageBreakToken>
</emphasis>
); ditto, 10773C (LL♀); ditto, 10777 (LL♀). 
<emphasis id="56F7A089391FF5150808F5FDE69B63EF" bold="true" pageId="27" pageNumber="28">Coahuila:</emphasis>
Sierra del Carmen, south peaks of range, NW side of upper Carboneras Canyon, 
<geoCoordinate id="A36EE6C2422BD81E60F57F3991DF4B21" degrees="28" direction="north" minutes="57" orientation="latitude" precision="925" value="28.95">28°57'N</geoCoordinate>
, 
<geoCoordinate id="28959876A9F970820973FEA758FAB828" degrees="102" direction="west" minutes="34" orientation="longitude" precision="925" value="-102.566666">102°34'W</geoCoordinate>
